<li>"Gaia" – 5:32</li>
<li>"Ananas" – 5:45</li>
<li>"Jump Up Behind Me" – 3:30</li>
<li>"Another Day" – 2:23</li>
<li>"Up Er Mei" – 3:49</li>
<li>"Up from Your Life" – 5:17</li>
<li>"Yellow and Rose" – 4:55</li>
<li>"Boatman" (<a href="/wiki/Livingston_Taylor" title="Livingston Taylor">Livingston Taylor</a>, M. Taylor) – 3:59</li>
<li>"<a href="/wiki/Walkin%27_My_Baby_Back_Home_(song)" title="Walkin' My Baby Back Home (song)">Walking My Baby Back Home</a>" (<a href="/wiki/Fred_E._Ahlert" title="Fred E. Ahlert">Fred E. Ahlert</a>, <a href="/wiki/Roy_Turk" title="Roy Turk">Roy Turk</a>) – 2:27</li>
<li>"Hangnail" (also known as "Money O Money") – 2:24 [hidden "bonus" track]</li>
</ol>
